  head
    meta(charset='utf-8')
    meta(name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no')
    meta(name='description' content='')
    meta(name='author' content='')
    link(rel='icon' href='/docs/4.0/assets/img/favicons/favicon.ico')
    title Tạo mới sản phẩm
    link(rel='canonical' href='https://getbootstrap.com/docs/4.0/examples/checkout/')
    // Bootstrap core CSS
    link(rel="stylesheet", href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.6.0/css/all.min.css")
    link(href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous")
  .container
    .py-5.text-center
      h2 Tạo mới sản phẩm
      p.lead
        | Below is an example form built entirely with Bootstrap&apos;s form controls. Each required form group has a validation state that can be triggered by attempting to submit the form without completing it.
    .row
      .col-md-4.order-md-2.mb-4
        h4.d-flex.justify-content-between.align-items-center.mb-3
          span.text-muted Your cart
          span.badge.badge-secondary.badge-pill 3
        ul.list-group.mb-3
          li.list-group-item.d-flex.justify-content-between.lh-condensed
            div
              h6.my-0 Product name
              small.text-muted Brief description
            span.text-muted $12
          li.list-group-item.d-flex.justify-content-between.lh-condensed
            div
              h6.my-0 Second product
              small.text-muted Brief description
            span.text-muted $8
          li.list-group-item.d-flex.justify-content-between.lh-condensed
            div
              h6.my-0 Third item
              small.text-muted Brief description
            span.text-muted $5
          li.list-group-item.d-flex.justify-content-between.bg-light
            .text-success
              h6.my-0 Promo code
              small EXAMPLECODE
            span.text-success -$5
          li.list-group-item.d-flex.justify-content-between
            span Total (USD)
            strong $20
        form.card.p-2
          .input-group
            input.form-control(type='text' placeholder='Promo code')
            .input-group-append
              button.btn.btn-secondary(type='submit') Redeem
      .col-md-8.order-md-1
        h4.mb-3 Thông tin sản phẩm
        form.needs-validation(novalidate='' action='/admin/product/create' method='POST' enctype="multipart/form-data")
          .mb-3
            label(for='title')
              | Tên sản phẩm 
            input#title.form-control(type='title' name='title' placeholder='Nhập tên sản phẩm...' required='')
            .invalid-feedback
              | Vui lòng nhập tên sảm phẩm.
          .mb-3
            label(for='des')
              | Mô tả
              span.text-muted (Tùy chọn)
            textarea#des.form-control(type='text' name='description' placeholder='Nhập mô tả...')
          .row
            .col-md-4.mb-3
              label(for='price') Giá (VNĐ)
              input#price.form-control(type='number' name='price' placeholder='' value='' required='')
              .invalid-feedback
                | Vui lòng nhập giá bán.
            .col-md-4.mb-3
              label(for='sales') Giảm giá (%)
              input#sales.form-control(type='text' name='discountPercentage' placeholder='' value='0' required='' min='0' max='100')
              .invalid-feedback
                | Vui lòng nhập % giảm giá.
            .col-md-4.mb-3
              label(for='stock') Số lượng kho
              input#stock.form-control(type='number' name='stock' placeholder='' value='' required='')
              .invalid-feedback
                | Vui lòng nhập số lượng kho.
          .row
            .col-md-6.mb-3
              label(for='status') Trạng thái
              select#status.custom-select.d-block.w-100.p-1(name='status' required='')
                option(value='active') Hoạt động
                option(value='disabled') Dừng hoạt động
              .invalid-feedback
                | Vui lòng chọn trạng thái.
            .col-md-6.mb-3
              label(for='thumbnail') Ảnh
              input#thumbnail.form-control.upload-img(type='file' name='thumbnail' placeholder='' value='' required='')
              .invalid-feedback
                | Vui lòng chèn thêm ảnh.
          .my-3.upload-img-preview(style="display: none;")
            img(src='' width='50%')
          
          button.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg.btn-block(type='submit') Tạo mới
    footer.my-5.pt-5.text-muted.text-center.text-small
      p.mb-1 &copy; 2017-2018 Company Name
      ul.list-inline
        li.list-inline-item
          a(href='#') Privacy
        li.list-inline-item
          a(href='#') Terms
        li.list-inline-item
          a(href='#') Support
